  <section name="Overview">
    <p>
     SMTPHandler is a handler for the 
     <a href="http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.5.0/docs/guide/logging/index.html">java.util.logging</a> library.  
     The handler sends <a href="http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.5.0/docs/api/java/util/logging/LogRecord.html">LogRecord</a>'s 
     via email using the <a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2821.txt">Simple Mail Transfer Protocol</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
	    This project is discussed in <a href="http://www.onjava.com/pub/a//onjava/2004/09/29/smtp-logging.html">
		    "Reporting Application Errors by Email"</a>
    </p>
